This script combines the features of several scripts/extensions (See contributors section). Its main purpose is to make use of any translation service in a fast and comfortable way without having to leave the page you are reading by showing a panel with the translation result. The panel is used to show the translation result of the currently selected text and/or the clipboard content. It can also translate the entire page with a single click on the icon inside the URL bar.

